td.p: The image is uised tae identify the organization Pizza Hut, a subject o public interest. The signeeficance o the logo is tae help the reader identify the organization, assure the readers that thay hae reached the richt airticle containin creetical commentar aboot the organization, an illustrate the organization's intendit brandin message in a way that wirds alone could nae convey.
